html:
Method

Description

Execute()

Runs a business process. Passes a key-value collection of input business process parameters where key is the parameter code (the Code property value) and the value is the parameter value. Returns the process execution result.

ExecProcElByUId()

Executes a specific business process element. Can only execute an element of a running process.
